<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>마이페이지 로그인 - Photo Diary</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm mb-4">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/">
            <i class="bi bi-camera-fill"></i> Photo Diary
        </a>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-circle display-4 text-primary"></i>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mt-2">마이페이지</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small">주문하실 때 입력한 이름을 입력해주세요.</p>
                </div>
                <form action="/mypage/login" method="post">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="name" class="form-label fw-bold">이름</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="name" name="name"
                               placeholder="예: 홍길동" required autofocus>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg fw-bold">확인</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
